bn Sulaiman, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cConcern about the world is a darkness in the heart, and concern about the Hereafter is a light in the heart.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd li-Ibn Ab\u012b Duny\u0101 543 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064f\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17418,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/01\/believer-shaded-sadaqah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37185,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Believers will be shaded by their charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, charity will extinguish the heat of the graves for their people. Only the believer can seek shade on the Day of Resurrection in the shade of his charity.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 3076 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17347,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/28\/worst-people-graves-masajid\/","url_meta":{"origin":37185